This E-Commerce platform was designed with role-based functionalities, catering to both admins and customers. Meanwhile, customers enjoyed a user-friendly interface to browse products, add items to their cart, and complete purchases hassle-free.It is a dynamic e-commerce platform using C# , ASP.NET, MVC.
